
"Thank you once again." He said. The driver nodded and left. Johnny walked back into the room he had placed Samantha and laid down on the couch. He was too tired to walk across the suite into his own half. As his eyes closed and he drifted off to sleep, he couldn't help but think of the girl that he had started to fall in love with. He thought of his costar sleeping in the bed across from him and drifted off to sleep with a smile on his face.